   "text": "Here I am in this park"
  },
  {
   "start": 511.66,
   "end": 515.74,
   "text": "Which is this park"
  },
  {
   "start": 515.74,
   "end": 519.26,
   "text": "And it's not actually the biggest park in Sofia"
  },
  {
   "start": 519.26,
   "end": 521.9,
   "text": "There's actually lots of parks"
  },
  {
   "start": 521.9,
   "end": 522.78,
   "text": "Like you could say"
  },
  {
   "start": 523.82,
   "end": 525.66,
   "text": "That park's bigger and that's in Sofia"
  },
  {
   "start": 525.66,
   "end": 527.1,
   "text": "So anyways"
  },
  {
   "start": 527.1,
   "end": 527.58,
   "text": "It's like"
  },
  {
   "start": 528.06,
   "end": 528.86,
   "text": "So we're like in a"
  },
  {
   "start": 529.82,
   "end": 532.3,
   "text": "So this park is pretty much just totally inside of Sofia"
  },
  {
   "start": 533.98,
   "end": 535.58,
   "text": "So we're in like a forest"
  },
  {
   "start": 536.14,
   "end": 540.38,
   "text": "That's cool"
  },
  {
   "start": 543.42,
   "end": 544.62,
   "text": "There's a tunnel right there"
  },
  {
   "start": 544.62,
   "end": 546.7,
   "text": "And then there's like a narrow foresty path"
  },
  {
   "start": 546.7,
   "end": 548.38,
   "text": "To this outdoor place where you had beers"
  },
  {
   "start": 549.18,
   "end": 550.06,
   "text": "I don't want to do that"
  },
  {
   "start": 551.34,
   "end": 552.46,
   "text": "And then this goes way off"
  },
  {
   "start": 552.46,
   "end": 554.46,
   "text": "It kind of reminds me of Vienna, Austria"
  },
  {
   "start": 555.74,
   "end": 557.1,
   "text": "Because the park there was really big"
  },
  {
   "start": 557.66,
   "end": 558.62,
   "text": "It's really thick"
  },
  {
   "start": 558.62,
   "end": 562.06,
   "text": "It's just like natural vegetation"
  },
  {
   "start": 562.06,
   "end": 563.42,
   "text": "It looks like a rain forest"
  },
  {
   "start": 563.42,
   "end": 564.78,
   "text": "And there's a trail that goes through there"
  },
  {
   "start": 566.22,
   "end": 568.06,
   "text": "Pretty place for the stormy kids to hang out"
  },
  {
   "start": 570.22,
   "end": 573.1,
   "text": "And it's thick"
  },
  {
   "start": 573.1,
   "end": 574.7,
   "text": "We're at 1,800 meters"
  },
  {
   "start": 575.5,
   "end": 576.86,
   "text": "I mean 1,800 feet"
  },
  {
   "start": 578.54,
   "end": 580.46,
   "text": "At like 43 degrees north"
  },
  {
   "start": 580.46,
   "end": 580.7,
   "text": "So"
  },
  {
   "start": 584.78,
   "end": 587.1,
   "text": "It seems a little foresty to me"
  },
  {
   "start": 587.1,
   "end": 587.82,
   "text": "That's pretty cool"
  },
  {
   "start": 592.94,
   "end": 594.38,
   "text": "This place is really cool man"
  },
  {
   "start": 595.66,
   "end": 601.25,
   "text": "It's just jungle in the middle of Sofia"
  },
  {
   "start": 605.82,
   "end": 607.5,
   "text": "With these trails to the four corners"
  },
  {
   "start": 608.94,
   "end": 609.34,
   "text": "And then"
  },
  {
   "start": 610.7,
   "end": 612.54,
   "text": "And then you have quarterly trails going off"
  },
  {
   "start": 613.98,
   "end": 615.66,
   "text": "In an octagarian fashion"
  },
  {
   "start": 616.86,
   "end": 617.42,
   "text": "That one"
  },
  {
   "start": 617.42,
   "end": 618.78,
   "text": "That little one that I came from"
  },
  {
   "start": 619.9,
   "end": 620.86,
   "text": "That one doesn't have one"
  },
  {
   "start": 620.86,
   "end": 621.58,
   "text": "But that one does"
  },
  {
   "start": 621.58,
   "end": 623.74,
   "text": "I'm going to cruise down here"
  },
  {
   "start": 625.42,
   "end": 627.66,
   "text": "Here I am in that forest riding my bike"
  },
  {
   "start": 628.86,
   "end": 631.1,
   "text": "Exploring one of the side paths"
  },
  {
   "start": 632.7,
   "end": 633.18,
   "text": "So cool"
  },
  {
   "start": 633.18,
   "end": 634.3,
   "text": "I'd love to do bike touring"
  },
  {
   "start": 634.3,
   "end": 635.26,
   "text": "Through something like this"
  },
  {
   "start": 635.26,
   "end": 636.38,
   "text": "For like hundreds of miles"
  },
  {
   "start": 638.46,
   "end": 639.98,
   "text": "Just emerge from the trail there"
  },
  {
   "start": 640.86,
   "end": 642.14,
   "text": "And boom into this area"
  },
  {
   "start": 642.14,
   "end": 643.5,
   "text": "Look where I am"
  },
  {
   "start": 644.86,
   "end": 645.9,
   "text": "It's like little kids"
  },
  {
